{"tid":2326630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"3歲妹超瘋《鬼滅》！早起做這事　媽看傻：這不是妳祖先欸","createTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:00:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b447c478b5421f132659b6584ef6b648c758d4","tid":2326630,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"日本人氣動漫「鬼滅之刃」改編的動畫電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》，在上映後創下票房奇蹟，《鬼滅之刃》也成為熱門話題，裏頭的角色更晉升成許多大人小孩的偶像。日本一名媽媽就分享，自己的女兒因為「過度熱愛」《鬼滅之刃》，竟還將海報貼在牆壁上，早上起床時雙手合十對著膜拜，虔誠的模樣讓網友看了全笑翻，忍不住直呼「卡哇依！」<br />\n<br />\n日本一名媽媽在推特發文，上傳兩張3歲女兒的照片，無奈地說「這些人不是你的祖先阿」！照片中，只見剛起床的小女兒，穿著睡衣、頭髮還相當凌亂，居然在迷矇之間，先對著牆壁上的畫像雙手合十，虔誠的鞠躬膜拜，讓媽媽看傻，因為牆上掛著的畫像並非女童的家人，而是卡通《鬼滅之刃》的角色們。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/15/2936943-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F15%2F2936943-PH.jpg&h=327ddeaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女童睡醒之後，居然先膜拜《鬼滅之刃》的人物畫像。（圖／翻攝自@chibi0u0chibi推特）<br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後，日本網友也全笑翻，貼文吸引21.7萬人按讚、2.9萬人轉推，大家看了都紛紛留言，「超級可愛」、「我支持她」、「這個海報我家也有」、「快要被融化了」、「鬼滅就是真理阿」、「海報還是黑白的哈哈哈」、「女兒：希望能傳授我呼吸的招式」、「難道這是『鬼滅教』」。<br />\n<br />\n也有網友認出，牆上貼的畫像其實是《鬼滅之刃》的「小彩蛋」，出版社在《鬼滅之刃》漫畫最後一集的發行日，買下日本《讀賣新聞》、《朝日新聞》、《每日新聞》、《產經新聞》、《日本經濟新聞》共5家全國發行的早報版面，刊登出角色的全版畫像，也掀起粉絲的蒐集熱潮。"},{"pid":"4cfbf65115554d54238e509c8ec55714612927d1","tid":2326630,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"死乖女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff96cff20f1ed57afee5857248571c73b5812aa","tid":2326630,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca8b83aa11313a3b9f5bc027ff612fd3975ee35","tid":2326630,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:29:23.000Z","msg":"偶神當神拜 追星必做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n妹妹從小養成習慣"},{"pid":"8ccacf9cea9b3a478676a97db92c46861e2bdd06","tid":2326630,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cfbf65115554d54238e509c8ec55714612927d1","tid":2326630,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"死乖女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"死女包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80aa3df937d65ad5b5bf0d4ab9d892770d639475","tid":2326630,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ff96cff20f1ed57afee5857248571c73b5812aa","tid":2326630,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"Like me<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336e9bf88b258773381ec1396935f2460a92084b","tid":2326630,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"可咩愛<br />\n老母應該教教佢啦屌"},{"pid":"4abce2c54c8bf9821e8c950a35a9cb9ea597b2fa","tid":2326630,"uid":209890,"like":2,"dis